	dprr:hasNoteText "Fast. Cap. (names entire); Polyb. 1.17.6; Chr. 354; Fast. Hyd. (Albino et Vituitulo); Chr. Pasc. ({Gr}); Cassiod.; Zon. 8.10; Degrassi, 40f., 115, 432f. Both Consuls besieged and finally captured the town of Agrigentum (Polyb. 1.17.6-20.2; Diod. 23.7-9; Zon. 8.10; cf. Naev. fr. 19;\n     Frontin. Str. 2.1.4)." .
